data.description: Looking for a well kept and beautiful neighborhood for your family and a neighborhood that will protect the value of your property?  How about a community swimming pool, lots of lakes, picnic area, quiet streets, friendly neighbors, etc.?  Then, Suncoast Lakes should receive a lot of your attention.  Ask your agent for the attached SUNCOAST LAKES HOMEOWNER’S BROCHURE.  5 bedrooms with 4 ½ baths will accommodate any family’s needs, especially when you add in a large living/dining room combo, a spacious great room, tons of kitchen cabinets and countertop space, lots of storage, and the 2nd floor loft.  Don’t need 5 bedrooms?  Just think what a wonderful office or hobby room a large bedroom would make.  The loft and family room give you 2 separate locations to relax and/or watch TV, which is especially convenient if the family doesn’t agree on what to do or watch.  How about a roomy, complete office in the loft?  3 bedrooms have ensuite baths, nice for family and even nicer for overnight guests.  This great setup has one bedroom on the first floor which is very accommodating for those whose climbing stairs days are over (or wish they were over).  Wood cabinets, upgraded granite countertops, and 2 pantry closets make this kitchen a homemaker’s delight.  Much, much more info is attached – ask your agent for copies, especially the FEATURES LIST.  Click the Tour 1 icon above for the NARRATED, VIDEO VIRTUAL TOUR (not just the same still photos)!  This property comes with a ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY.  The reasonable HOA fee includes all the usual expenditures plus cable TV and irrigation water – big savings.  This property is not in a flood hazard zone and has a NEW roof in March 2023 – more savings. Seller will do no repairs.
